福尔摩斯 我们得立刻送你上医院
Holmes, we must get you to a hospital at once.

566
00:38:47,685 --> 00:38:50,117
不 和我保持距离
No, Now keep your distance!

567
00:38:50,192 --> 00:38:51,995
你不知道这病是会传染的么
Don't you see this thing is contagious?

568
00:38:52,072 --> 00:38:54,646
你觉得我会在意这个么?
Do you think such a consideration weighs with me?

569
00:38:54,718 --> 00:38:56,819
离我远点!
Keep your distance!

570
00:38:57,851 --> 00:39:01,090
这病可能会传遍整个伦敦
This could run through London.

571
00:39:18,810 --> 00:39:20,400
是痉挛
It's cramps.

572
00:39:20,481 --> 00:39:21,889
福尔摩斯?
Holmes?

573
00:39:26,260 --> 00:39:27,755
非要请医生的话
If I had a doctor at least

574
00:39:27,827 --> 00:39:30,854
至少得请个让我信得过的
let me have someone whom I have confidence?

575
00:39:30,926 --> 00:39:32,623
你信不过我?
You have none in me?

576
00:39:32,702 --> 00:39:33,639
你的友情 当然信得过
Your friendship, yes.

577
00:39:33,639 --> 00:39:35,825
可你只是一名普通的执业医师
But you're only a general practitioner

578
00:39:35,826 --> 00:39:38,330
经验不足
with mediocre qualifications.

579
00:39:38,515 --> 00:39:40,913
你的这评论可不足取 福尔摩斯
That remark is unworthy of you, Holmes.

580
00:39:40,988 --> 00:39:43,436
它清楚地向我表明了 你神经焦躁不安的状态
It shows me very clearly the state of your nerves.

581
00:39:43,436 --> 00:39:45,449
它证明了你的无知
That demonstrates your ignorance.

582
00:39:45,450 --> 00:39:47,559
你对塔帕努里(印尼地名)热病 知道多少?
What do you know about Tapanuli Fever?

583
00:39:47,638 --> 00:39:49,927
你知道福摩萨(葡萄牙人对台湾的称呼) 黑色败血症么?
What do you know about Black Formosa corruption?

584
00:39:50,005 --> 00:39:51,499
我从来没有听过这两种病
I have never heard of either.

585
00:39:51,571 --> 00:39:55,440
这是东方奇怪的病症
That is strange pathological disorders in the east.

586
00:39:55,441 --> 00:39:57,657
要是你信不过我 我去请Jasper Meek
If you have no faith in me, let me fetch Jasper Meek.

587
00:39:57,658 --> 00:39:59,529
还有Penrose Fisher 另外Ainstree也在伦敦
Penrose Fisher, Ainstree is here in London.

588
00:39:59,530 --> 00:40:00,776
我去把他找来
Let me fetch him.

589
00:40:01,584 --> 00:40:04,394
只有一个人能帮助我
There's only one man who can help me.

590
00:40:05,114 --> 00:40:07,582
一个被我们中伤过的人
It's a man we have maligned.

591
00:40:08,386 --> 00:40:10,658
Culverton Smith? 你相信他会帮忙么?
Culverton Smith? Do you believe he would help?

592
00:40:10,659 --> 00:40:12,128
他必须帮
He must.

593
00:40:13,886 --> 00:40:15,939
这是我唯一的机会了
It is my only chance.

594
00:40:19,112 --> 00:40:20,978
牡蛎
Oysters,

595
00:40:23,462 --> 00:40:25,505
它们真的会繁殖 不是么?
they do breed don't they?

596
00:40:26,457 --> 00:40:28,711
我不能想象整个海底
I cannot think that the whole bottom of the ocean

597
00:40:28,789 --> 00:40:32,057
就是一团硬硬的牡蛎
is one solid mass of oysters.

598
00:40:34,047 --> 00:40:37,733
福尔摩斯 你能听见我说话么?
Holmes, can you hear me?

599
00:40:39,860 --> 00:40:43,687
我马上就出门去找Culverton Smith
I'm going for Culverton Smith this instant.

600
00:40:43,830 --> 00:40:45,723
那你去吧
Then go.

601
00:40:46,093 --> 00:40:48,804
我会把他带回来的
I'm to bring him back here with me.

602
00:40:49,192 --> 00:40:52,873
他是研究洪水热的专家
He's the emperor of river fevers,

603
00:40:52,951 --> 00:40:54,684
你要说服他来这里
of course you must persuade him

604
00:40:54,762 --> 00:40:57,013
但你得找个借口先回来
but you must return alone.

605
00:40:58,278 --> 00:41:02,064
随便什么借口 别跟他一起回来
Any excuse not to come with him.

606
00:41:02,143 --> 00:41:06,137
跟他说我很抱歉 真的很抱歉
Tell him I apologize, I do.

607
00:41:06,634 --> 00:41:08,944
别让我失望 华生
Don't fail me Watson.

608
00:41:09,071 --> 00:41:10,934
当然不会的
Of course not.

609
00:41:15,093 --> 00:41:17,405
那些河流里
And what of rivers.

610
00:41:19,237 --> 00:41:20,958
没有天敌
Are there no natural enemies

611
00:41:20,959 --> 00:41:24,047
来限制那些生物的繁殖么?
to limit the increase of these creatures?

612
00:41:26,548 --> 00:41:28,477
可怕
It's horrible,

613
00:41:29,508 --> 00:41:31,758
太可怕了
horrible.

614
00:41:43,503 --> 00:41:45,413
我要见Culverton Smith 这事很重要
It's essential that I see Mr. Culverton Smith.

615
00:41:45,488 --> 00:41:47,018
先生 Culverton Smith先生
Mr. Culverton Smith, sir,

616
00:41:47,089 --> 00:41:48,441
不希望在他工作时
does not appreciate being disturbed

617
00:41:48,516 --> 00:41:49,906
有人打扰
during his hours of study.

618
00:41:49,979 --> 00:41:52,057
-等一下 您不能... -Smith!
-Just a minute sir, you can't just... -Smith!

619
00:41:52,057 --> 00:41:53,160
先生
Sir!

620
00:41:53,635 --> 00:41:54,429
Smith!
Smith!

621
00:41:54,505 --> 00:41:55,830
别这样 先生!
Please sir!

622
00:41:56,037 --> 00:41:56,952
Smith!
Smith!

623
00:41:56,952 --> 00:41:58,783
先生 您不能这样
Sir, you can't just,

624
00:41:58,856 --> 00:42:00,831
您不能进去 先生
you can't just walk in, sir.

625
00:42:07,666 --> 00:42:09,255
噢 Smith
Ah, Smith.

626
00:42:09,337 --> 00:42:11,744
您这么做是要干什么 先生?
What the devil do you mean by this, sir?

627
00:42:11,744 --> 00:42:14,039
我是为了歇洛克 福尔摩斯来的
I've come from Sherlock Holmes.

628
00:42:14,496 --> 00:42:16,516
他病的很重
He is desperately ill,

629
00:42:16,517 --> 00:42:17,993
他请求您去看看他
and he begs you to come to him.

630
00:42:18,075 --> 00:42:19,178
为什么?
Why?

631
00:42:19,259 --> 00:42:21,757
您就是个医生 可以照顾他
You are a physician, tend to him yourself.

632
00:42:21,757 --> 00:42:24,936
他相信你是唯一能救他的人
He believes that you are the only man who can save him.

633
00:42:25,456 --> 00:42:26,974
救他?
Save him?

634
00:42:27,128 --> 00:42:28,984
我求你来看看吧
I beg you to come.

635
00:42:29,355 --> 00:42:31,123
他感染了什么病了?
What has he contracted?

636
00:42:31,201 --> 00:42:33,977
他想就是害死你表弟的那种热病
He thinks it is the fever which killed your cousin.

637
00:42:34,056 --> 00:42:35,681
他怎么能染上那种病?
How did he come by it?

638
00:42:35,762 --> 00:42:37,315
他去过Rotherhithe
He has been in Rotherhithe.

639
00:42:37,398 --> 00:42:39,759
噢
Ah,

640
00:42:39,834 --> 00:42:41,742
真令人遗憾
I'm sorry to hear this.

641
00:42:42,933 --> 00:42:44,740
我希望您弄错了
I hope you are wrong.

642
00:42:45,126 --> 00:42:47,385
尽管那天他侮辱了我
Despite his insulting behavior the other day,

643
00:42:47,386 --> 00:42:49,923
我仍旧尊重他的才智
I have every respect for his talents.

644
00:42:50,245 --> 00:42:51,906
他的业余爱好是研究犯罪
He's an amateur of crime

645
00:42:51,985 --> 00:42:53,881
就像我的业余爱好是研究疾病
as I am of disease.

646
00:42:54,388 --> 00:42:56,413
坏人之于他
For him the villain,

647
00:42:56,413 --> 00:42:58,902
仿佛细菌之于我
for me the microbe.

648
00:42:59,994 --> 00:43:02,182
这里是我的囚徒
Here are my prisoners.

649
00:43:02,499 --> 00:43:05,003
在这些培养基的明胶里
Among these gelatin cultivations,

650
00:43:05,075 --> 00:43:08,268
有世界上最凶恶的犯人在服刑
some of the worst offenders in the world are doing time.

651
00:43:08,349 --> 00:43:09,939
求你了 已经没有时间可以浪费了
Please, please, there is no time to lose.

652
00:43:10,019 --> 00:43:11,127
他都病得快死了
He is desperately ill.

653
00:43:11,128 --> 00:43:13,650
这跟我有什么相干?
Of what consequence is that to me?

654
00:43:15,311 --> 00:43:17,286
他用最无礼的态度对我造谣中伤
He maligned me in the most outrageous manner.

655
00:43:17,286 --> 00:43:20,066
他为此感到后悔 他一直在重复这一点
He, he regrets it, he was most  insistent upon that point.

656
00:43:20,066 --> 00:43:23,339
他知道热病在Rotherhithe流行
He knows that the fever was abroad in Rotherhithe.

657
00:43:26,227 --> 00:43:27,419
他病了有多久了?
How long has he been ill?

658
00:43:27,496 --> 00:43:28,973
三天了
Three days.

659
00:43:29,202 --> 00:43:30,448
他有没有神智昏迷 胡言乱语?
Is he delirious?

660
00:43:30,526 --> 00:43:32,603
有时候很严重
Sometimes seriously so.

661
00:43:32,684 --> 00:43:34,609
我立刻随你一起去
I will come with you at once.

662
00:43:34,609 --> 00:43:36,164
我另外还约了点事情 先生
I have another appointment, sir.

663
00:43:36,235 --> 00:43:37,134
那好 我就自己去
Very well, I shall go alone.

664
00:43:37,135 --> 00:43:40,565
最多半个小时 我就会到
Staples, you can rely on my being there in a half an hour at most.

665
00:43:43,726 --> 00:43:44,755
你见到他了么?
Did you see him?

666
00:43:44,835 --> 00:43:45,844
是的 他正在赶来
Yes, he's coming.

667
00:43:45,914 --> 00:43:47,682
你是最好的信使
Ah, you're the best of messengers.

668
00:43:47,760 --> 00:43:50,263
你可以离开这里了
You can disappear from the scene now.

669
00:43:50,336 --> 00:43:51,866
我应该留下来听听他的意见 福尔摩斯
I should stay to hear his opinion, Holmes,

670
00:43:51,938 --> 00:43:52,728
真的很有必要
I really should.

671
00:43:52,728 --> 00:43:54,720
他敏感的近乎病态
No reason he is morbidly sensitive.

672
00:43:54,793 --> 00:43:56,323
我们必须让他独自展现他的技艺
We must let him practice his arts alone.

673
00:43:56,394 --> 00:43:58,503
-亲爱的福尔摩斯 -前门有动静
-My dear, Holmes. -That's the front door,

674
00:43:59,040 --> 00:44:00,198
是他
It's him.

675
00:44:00,199 --> 00:44:01,088
快藏起来
Hide.

676
00:44:01,088 --> 00:44:02,101
藏起来
Hide.

677
00:44:02,102 --> 00:44:03,971
快 如果你爱我的话
Quick, if you love me.

678
00:44:28,250 --> 00:44:30,303
福尔摩斯?
Holmes?

679
00:44:52,308 --> 00:44:54,489
福尔摩斯?
Holmes?

680
00:44:54,636 --> 00:44:57,125
哦 Smith 我不敢奢望你能来
Oh, Smith, I hardly dared to hope.

681
00:44:57,125 --> 00:44:58,970
我也想不到
I should imagine not.

682
00:44:59,132 --> 00:45:01,042
看 我还是来了
Yet you see I'm here.

683
00:45:01,116 --> 00:45:02,670
要以德报怨 福尔摩斯
Coals of fire Holmes,

684
00:45:02,753 --> 00:45:04,069
以德报怨 (coals of fire典出圣经 撒下22:13)
coals of fire.

685
00:45:04,145 --> 00:45:05,842
真是高尚
It's noble.

686
00:45:05,921 --> 00:45:07,024
你知道你得了什么病么?
Do you know what is wrong with you?

687
00:45:07,104 --> 00:45:07,740
是的
Yes.

688
00:45:07,740 --> 00:45:09,333
你知道这些症状么?
You recognize the symptoms?

689
00:45:09,333 --> 00:45:10,682
是的 很清楚
Yes, quite well.

690
00:45:10,761 --> 00:45:11,769
那你是病了三天了?
Three days with you then?

691
00:45:11,839 --> 00:45:12,455
是的
Yes.

692
00:45:12,455 --> 00:45:13,604
你坚持的不错
You have lasted well.

693
00:45:13,604 --> 00:45:15,594
到这天Victor就已经死了
With Victor it was all over by now.

694
00:45:15,669 --> 00:45:17,294
我注意到了这点
I have noticed this,

695
00:45:17,375 --> 00:45:20,710
越是成熟冷静 坚持的越久
the more mature coolies seems to last longer.

696
00:45:20,787 --> 00:45:22,606
请给我水 给我水喝
Water please. Could I have some water?

697
00:45:22,607 --> 00:45:24,194
哦 最后的口渴
Oh, the final thirst.

698
00:45:25,661 --> 00:45:27,367
你快要完了
You're near the end.

699
00:45:33,913 --> 00:45:36,246
请帮帮我 尽你所能帮帮我
Please help me, help me if you can.

700
00:45:38,751 --> 00:45:40,970
我可以替你隐瞒你的动机
I could champion your cause.

701
00:45:41,050 --> 00:45:42,042
我的动机?
My cause?

702
00:45:42,043 --> 00:45:43,355
你的工作
Your work.

703
00:45:43,355 --> 00:45:44,979
它应该广为宣传
It deserves to be trumpeted.

704
00:45:45,053 --> 00:45:46,821
我可以为你效劳
I could be of service.

705
00:45:46,899 --> 00:45:48,429
我很怀疑
I doubt it.

706
00:45:48,500 --> 00:45:49,429
多亏了你
Thanks to you

707
00:45:49,429 --> 00:45:52,760
给我名誉带来了不可弥补的损害
the damage done to my reputation is irreparable.

708
00:45:52,760 --> 00:45:55,902
你是说Victor Savage
You mean Victor Savage,

709
00:45:55,985 --> 00:45:56,699
你的表弟
your cousin,

710
00:45:56,699 --> 00:45:58,812
我都已经忘了
I had forgotten that.

711
00:45:59,362 --> 00:46:01,651
你也被牵涉进来了么?
Did you, were you involved?

712
00:46:01,731 --> 00:46:03,182
我有点不确定了
I couldn't be sure.

713
00:46:08,798 --> 00:46:12,690
大侦探也有不清楚的时候
The great detective couldn't be sure.

714
00:46:12,767 --> 00:46:15,348
就算你知道Savage是怎么死的 也没有关系
Well it doesn't matter to me if you know how Savage died.

715
00:46:15,349 --> 00:46:17,114
你是不会坐在证人席上了
I don't see you in the witness box,

716
00:46:17,188 --> 00:46:19,836
只可能是躺在另外一种盒子里
quite another sort of box.

717
00:46:24,987 --> 00:46:27,384
就在他吸鸦片吸得不省人事的时候
I put an infected mosquito to his neck

718
00:46:27,459 --> 00:46:30,087
我在他的脖子上放了一只受感染的蚊子
while he was in an opiate stupor.

719
00:46:31,776 --> 00:46:33,583
就是这样
There.

720
00:46:35,292 --> 00:46:36,746
但是你
But you,

721
00:46:37,068 --> 00:46:39,640
你又是怎么被传染的?
how did you come to contract it?

722
00:46:39,992 --> 00:46:41,468
你那个来找我的同伴
That fellow who came for me

723
00:46:41,469 --> 00:46:44,366
告诉我说你是在Rotherhithe被传染的
told me you thought you caught it in Rotherhithe.

724
00:46:44,449 --> 00:46:46,952
我只能这么认为
Oh, I can only account for it, so.

725
00:46:47,026 --> 00:46:48,970
好好回想一下
Cast your mind back.

726
00:46:49,043 --> 00:46:51,513
-痉挛? -是的
-Cramps? -Oh, yes.

727
00:46:51,514 --> 00:46:53,404
-帮帮我 -我会的
-Help me. -I will.

728
00:46:54,511 --> 00:46:55,685
疼痛
The pain.

729
00:46:55,763 --> 00:46:58,576
死之前总是
Yes, the coolies used to do some squealing

730
00:46:58,653 --> 00:47:00,088
伴随着哀号
before the end.

731
00:47:01,091 --> 00:47:02,669
好吧
Well now.

732
00:47:06,174 --> 00:47:08,463
在几天前 你还没有发病的时候
A few days before your symptoms began

733
00:47:08,541 --> 00:47:11,388
你是不是收到过什么邮件
did you receive anything by post?

734
00:47:11,466 --> 00:47:12,711
我想不起来了
I can't think.

735
00:47:12,788 --> 00:47:14,592
一个包裹?
A parcel?

736
00:47:14,668 --> 00:47:15,396
你收到了
You did.

737
00:47:16,142 --> 00:47:17,898
是的 一些烟草的样品
Yes, samples of tobacco.

738
00:47:17,898 --> 00:47:19,239
没错
That's right.

739
00:47:19,239 --> 00:47:22,246
你没有注意那个盒子的结构么?
Did you notice the construction of the box?

740
00:47:22,329 --> 00:47:23,574
在烟草下面
Under the tobacco,

741
00:47:23,652 --> 00:47:26,294
有两根小钉子伸了出来
two small tacks stuck out.

742
00:47:26,749 --> 00:47:28,314
你没有看到么?
You didn't see them?

743
00:47:32,320 --> 00:47:34,198
是它传染了热病么?
They were infected?

744
00:47:35,245 --> 00:47:37,249
你这傻瓜
You fool.

745
00:47:37,752 --> 00:47:40,816
你找我的茬 现在你玩完了
You would tangle with me and now you are finished.

746
00:47:44,158 --> 00:47:45,902
那个盒子
The box.

747
00:47:47,743 --> 00:47:49,306
现在在哪?
Where is it?

748
00:47:52,304 --> 00:47:53,599
在哪?
Where is it?

