影子越来越长了 是么?
The shadows begin to lengthen, do they?

752
00:48:05,569 --> 00:48:07,336
好的 我来拧亮点
Yes, I'll do that.

753
00:48:12,427 --> 00:48:15,169
我更喜欢在亮一点的灯光下看着你死去
I prefer to see you die in the light.

754
00:48:25,866 --> 00:48:27,281
在这里
There it is,

755
00:48:28,790 --> 00:48:31,977
你最后的一小点证据
your last shred of evidence.

756
00:48:32,134 --> 00:48:33,447
好了
Well, well,

757
00:48:34,082 --> 00:48:36,781
还有什么可以效劳的么 我的朋友
is there any other little service I can do you my friend?

758
00:48:36,781 --> 00:48:41,236
火柴 香烟会很棒
A match and a cigarette would be most welcome.

759
00:48:55,703 --> 00:48:58,710
三天不吃不喝是一回事
Three days without food and water is one thing,

760
00:48:59,846 --> 00:49:03,504
但是抽不上烟 就太痛苦了
but to be without tobacco I have found most irksome.

761
00:49:03,606 --> 00:49:05,441
探长 进来吧
Come in Inspector.

762
00:49:08,724 --> 00:49:10,713
以拧亮煤气灯为信号
By turning up the gas,

763
00:49:11,023 --> 00:49:15,288
Smith亲自发出了我们的信号
Smith was good enough to give our signal himself.

764
00:49:15,862 --> 00:49:19,291
他坦白谋杀了Victor Savage
This is the self-confessed murderer of Victor Savage.

765
00:49:19,292 --> 00:49:20,975
你可以信口开河 福尔摩斯
You may lie as you like Holmes.

766
00:49:20,975 --> 00:49:24,397
但你证明不了你精神错乱的猜想
You have no corroboration for you insane suspicions.

767
00:49:24,398 --> 00:49:28,972
华生 他身后有一个盒子
Watson, he has a box behind his back.

768
00:49:29,265 --> 00:49:31,882
小心点拿着
Treat it very gingerly

769
00:49:31,883 --> 00:49:33,482
千万别打开
and don't open it.

770
00:49:33,965 --> 00:49:35,219
去死吧
Damn you.

771
00:49:35,220 --> 00:49:37,117
-阻止他 -你去死吧
-Stop him. -Damn you.

772
00:50:01,783 --> 00:50:04,072
扮演一个角色最成功的办法
The best way of acting a part successfully

773
00:50:04,150 --> 00:50:05,191
就是成为这个角色
is to be it.

774
00:50:05,594 --> 00:50:06,863
要凡士林做什么?
What's the vaseline for?

775
00:50:06,864 --> 00:50:08,042
涂抹在额头
For the forehead.

776
00:50:09,024 --> 00:50:10,720
眼睛里滴些颠茄酊
Belladonna in the eyes.

777
00:50:11,949 --> 00:50:13,008
蜂蜡
Bee's wax.

778
00:50:13,009 --> 00:50:16,037
抹在嘴唇周围
Incrustation around the lips.

779
00:50:16,906 --> 00:50:19,179
为什么你不让我靠近你呢
Why wouldn't you let me near you,

780
00:50:19,260 --> 00:50:21,498
事实上你并没有被感染
when in truth there was no infection?

781
00:50:21,836 --> 00:50:24,991
你以为我看不起你的医道么?
Do you imagine that I have no respect for your medical talents?

782
00:50:24,992 --> 00:50:26,304
距离6英尺
At six feet

783
00:50:26,304 --> 00:50:28,240
我可以瞒过你
I could deceive you.

784
00:50:28,241 --> 00:50:30,212
但要是更近些
But any closer,

785
00:50:31,435 --> 00:50:32,511
你就会做出机敏的判断了
with your astute judgment,

786
00:50:32,511 --> 00:50:33,967
不 不 不
no, no, no, no.

787
00:50:34,893 --> 00:50:37,112
最重要的是
No it was essential,

788
00:50:37,190 --> 00:50:40,449
你和Hudson太太要相信我快死了
that you and Mrs. Hudson believed me to be at death's door

789
00:50:40,450 --> 00:50:43,872
不然Smith就像老鼠一样会有所察觉
otherwise Smith would have smelt a rat.

790
00:50:43,873 --> 00:50:44,960
老鼠
Rats,

791
00:50:44,960 --> 00:50:46,257
蜂蜡
bee's wax,

792
00:50:46,257 --> 00:50:47,598
福尔摩斯先生
Mr. Holmes,

793
00:50:47,598 --> 00:50:51,244
你是全伦敦最糟糕的房客了
you are the very worst tenant in London.

794
00:51:00,238 --> 00:51:02,824
Georgie说他要来保卫庄园
Georgie says he's going to guard the house.

795
00:51:02,955 --> 00:51:04,641
他们都是好孩子 Savage夫人
Oh they're fine children, Mrs. Savage.

796
00:51:04,641 --> 00:51:06,009
就像是小天使
They're little angels.

797
00:51:06,009 --> 00:51:09,367
这么多年来我们都是称为Savage家族
For years we're known as little savages.

798
00:51:14,771 --> 00:51:16,315
谢谢你 华生医生
Thank you, Dr. Watson,

799
00:51:16,315 --> 00:51:18,756
让我们回到家
for letting us keep our home.

800
00:51:19,143 --> 00:51:20,009
谢谢你 亲爱的
Thank you my dear.

801
00:51:20,010 --> 00:51:21,120
我很想接受这份荣誉
I'd like to take the credit

802
00:51:21,120 --> 00:51:24,358
但那属于福尔摩斯先生
but it belongs to Mr. Holmes.

803
00:51:37,248 --> 00:51:40,008
我们很感激您 先生
We are very grateful to you, sir.

804
00:51:43,201 --> 00:51:45,702
是我的荣幸 Savage小姐
My privilege, Miss. Savage.

